
    Package and deploy a WAR
* web apps packaged in a war file (web archive)
* war file --> zip file with a specific directory structure
* it contains servlets, JSPs, filters, listeners and static content (html, css, png, js)
* root dir
   -- WEB-INF
       -- web.xml --> configs in this file take precedence over annotations
       -- lib (libraries)
       -- classes
          - compiled servlet classes in their corresponding package
   -- META-INF (automatically generated)
       -- context.xml --> used by Tomcat to map a reference to a resource